        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Mineral Leasing Act regarding leases and royalties to provide that the royalty rate applicable to any soda ash lease shall be two percent during the five-year period beginning on the date of enactment of this Act. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
